		"description": "<p>In your flesh is whispered the secrets of fulgurian sovereignty. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<p><strong>Resist Electricity. </strong>You have resistance to lightning&nbsp;damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Lightning Reflection. </strong>If you would be dealt lightning damage, you can use your reaction to deflect it to a creature you can see within 30 feet (Dexterity save halves). The DC for this trait is 8 + your proficiency bonus + your choice of Constitution, Intelligence, Wisdom, or Charisma modifier. If the target is the one who dealt you lightning damage, they automatically fail their saving throw.</p>\n<p>Once you use this trait, you can&rsquo;t use it again until you complete a short or long rest.</p>",
